    "abstractNote": "This article offers the editio princeps and translation of the Armenian translation of an invocational prayer of a now lost memra of Jacob of Serugh on Good Friday and the destruction of Sheol. This text is different from the Armenian homily on Good Friday which was recently edited and translated by Edward G. Mathews, Jr. On the basis of comparisons with extant homilies of Jacob, it is argued that the prayer is genuine.",
